column1: # Readings for the following periods are apportioned:
# The following readings are estimates and have been omitted:
# The reading for January 1941 is estimated for snow and has been retained.
# The reading for March 1947 is estimated for snow and has been retained.
# The reading for December 1950 is estimated for snow and has been retained.
# The 1950s sheet gives the location as River Dove, although the grid reference and altitude put the gauge some distance from the river.
